    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus containing around 2,500 species of annual or perennial herbs, woody shrubs, or trees with a caustic, poisonous milky sap. It is one of the largest flowering-plant genera.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
